import React from 'react';
import { Typography } from '@material-ui/core';
import { Button } from '@material-ui/core';
import {Grid} from '@material-ui/core';
import ExpandMoreIcon from '@material-ui/icons/ExpandMore';
import Item from './Item.js';
import Scroll from './Scroll.js';
import Project from './Project.js';

const Projects = () => {
    return (
        <Grid container
        direction="row"
        justify="center"
        alignItems="center"
        style={{marginLeft:'30px', paddingRight:'30px'}}>

            <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Typography
                display="block"
                justifyContent="center"
                align="center"
                variant="h3"
                style={{opacity:'100%', fontWeight:'bold', fontSize:'40px', color:'black',
                 backgroundColor:'rgba(205, 255, 219,0.8)', height:'200px', paddingTop:'25%'}}>
                    Projects
                </Typography>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={6}>
                <Scroll
                    color='rgba(0,0,0,0.8)'
                    style={{paddingRight:'20px', paddingLeft:'20px'}}>

                <Grid container
                direction="row"
                justify="center"
                alignItems="center"
                spacing={3}>
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                    <Project />
                </Grid>
            </Scroll>

            </Grid>
            

        </Grid>
    )
}

export default Projects;
